31d3f13b-27d5-4291-9fb3-d5d5708a72f3.name: mysql_instance_endpoint
31d3f13b-27d5-4291-9fb3-d5d5708a72f3.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'mysql_instance_endpoint') as mysql_instance_endpoint
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name = 'mysql_uptime'
GROUP BY mysql_instance_endpoint
